H@Beak Mask is a Head Armor (Attire) in Bloodborne. It is part of the Crowfeather Set.

^d"Wood-carved mask of Eileen the Crow, Hunter of Hunters. The beak contains incense to mask scents of blood and beast." 
Hunters of Hunters dress as crows to suggest sky burial. 
The first Hunter of Hunters came from a foreign land, 
and gave the dead a virtuous native funeral ritual, 
rather than impose a blasphemous Yharnam burial service upon them, 
with the hope that former compatriots might be returned to the skies, 
and find rest in a hunter's dream. "

L@Bath Messengers in the Hunter's Dream after obtaining the Crow Hunter Badge.

^n"Resembles the mask of a seventeenth century plague doctor. 
Plague doctors also kept aromatic items in the beak of the mask 
as it was thought to ward off infection."

